<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Sender</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        form {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        input,
        textarea,
        button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 4px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        button {
            background-color: #4caf50;
            color: #fff;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <form action="/send-email" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
        <label for="sender">Sender Email:</label>
        <input type="email" id="sender" name="sender" value="mozzam607@gmail.com" required>

        <label for="recipient">Recipient Email:</label>
        <input type="email" id="recipient" name="recipient" value="{{recipient}}" required>

        <label for="subject">Subject:</label>
        <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" value="Python/Nodejs Developer" required>

        <label for="body">Body:</label>
        <textarea id="body" name="body" rows="4"
            required>I am a software developer with experience in building scalable web applications using Django, Python, and Node.js, along with a strong foundation in microservices architecture, machine learning, and cloud technologies. I have previously worked on building trading platforms, optimizing real-time data distribution, and enhancing system performance at a fintech company. My role included leveraging APIs and quantitative analysis to develop robust financial tools that improved data efficiency and reduced latency.Currently, I focus on developing AI-driven solutions for a CPaaS platform, where I work on enhancing communication systems through advanced analytics and machine learning models. This includes building sentiment analysis, keyword extraction, and speaker diarization features to improve customer support insights. My background enables me to deliver powerful solutions that blend financial expertise with advanced communication technology.With certifications in AWS, Azure, and Google Data Analytics, I continuously seek to expand my technical knowledge and contribute to the growth of innovative platforms.</textarea>

        <label for="attachment">Attachment:</label>
        <input type="file" id="attachment" name="attachment">

        <button type="submit">Send Email</button>
        <h3>{{successMessage}}</h3>
        <h3>{{errorMessage}}</h3>
    </form>

</body>

</html>
